    _TEST = {

        'md5': '9b0636f8c0f7614afa4ea5e4c6e57e83',

            'ext': 'mp4',
            'title': 'md5:35d42050a3ece241d5ddd7fdcc6fd896',
            'uploader': 'ytdl',
            'uploader_id': 'eGT5bab',
        },
    }

    def _real_extract(self, url):

        return {

            'title': self._og_search_description(webpage).strip(),
